    "en": {
      "description": {
        "text": "A small hilly island north of Härsö. Inside a large, pointed boulder that juts out of the water on the west side, there is a short but nice dihedral. On the left side of the wall, there’s an impressive crack. (Tip: Under the boulder, there is a cave furnished with a floor, table, and chairs.)",
